summary: Resourceful and accomplished Office Manager with extensive office operations and personnel organization expertise. Highlights include interpersonal skills, ability to work independently, handle pressure, meet deadlines, proficient managerial skills, effective team leader and efficient team player, excellent customer service skills, exemplary work ethic, multitasks, plans and organizes individual and corporate meetings, and excellent written and verbal communication skills. Skills include typing (70 WPM), dictaphone, transcription, speed writing, CaseNet, proficiency in Microsoft Word (95 through Word 2007), WordPerfect, Excel, Outlook, Access, PowerPoint, Timeslips, QuickBooks, calendaring, travel arrangements, itineraries, Proficient in using the Tickle System for legal and corporate matters, filing, fax machine, copiers, e-filing, multi-line telephone systems. Data entry (Superior), minutes of meetings, A/P - A/R.
